
Overview of adj spicy

The adj spicy has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                         
1. piquant, savory, savoury, spicy, zesty -- (having an agreeably pungent taste)
2. hot, spicy -- (producing a burning sensation on the taste nerves; "hot salsa"; "jalapeno peppers are very hot")
3. blue, gamy, gamey, juicy, naughty, racy, risque, spicy -- (suggestive of sexual impropriety; "a blue movie"; "blue jokes"; "he skips asterisks and gives you the gamy details"; "a juicy scandal"; "a naughty wink"; "naughty words"; "racy anecdotes"; "a risque story"; "spicy gossip")
